      Nice to meet you.
    </h1>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] gap-10 items-start">
      <div class="aspect-square w-40 md:w-full rounded-full bg-neutral-900 border border-white/10 overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Replace with real portrait when ready -->
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          My name is Baji Tumendemberel. I graduated from Yale University in 2022. I find my
